        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer591883893" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2272876131125176412">“Our twentieth century had inverted the story of Mohammed and the mountain; nowadays, the mountain came to the modern Mohammed.”<br/>Isn’t it about the modern mass media?<br/>“‘When I opened my eyes, I saw the Aleph.’ ‘The Aleph?’ ‘Yes, the only place on earth where all places are – seen from every angle, each standing clear, without any confusion or blending.’”<br/>As The Aleph is a locus of the entire world so the stories by <b>Jorge Luis Borges</b> are the epitome of the entire intellectual universe.<br/>“His guiding p</span>
  <span id="freeText2272876131125176412" style="display:none">“Our twentieth century had inverted the story of Mohammed and the mountain; nowadays, the mountain came to the modern Mohammed.”<br />Isn’t it about the modern mass media?<br />“‘When I opened my eyes, I saw the Aleph.’ ‘The Aleph?’ ‘Yes, the only place on earth where all places are – seen from every angle, each standing clear, without any confusion or blending.’”<br />As The Aleph is a locus of the entire world so the stories by <b>Jorge Luis Borges</b> are the epitome of the entire intellectual universe.<br />“His guiding purpose, though it was supernatural, was not impossible. He wanted to dream a man; he wanted to dream him down to the last detail and project him into the world of reality.”<br /><b>Jorge Luis Borges</b> has dreamt many of such men and they continue to live in his tales… Probably we are someone’s dreams too.</span>
  <a data-text-id="2272876131125176412" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
