        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2479917980" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10451631091396208229">I can&apos;t say I loved this book. However, there were short stories within it I loved, such as The Immortal and The House of Asterion. I simply didn&apos;t find most of the short stories interesting. Also, while I was reading this book I noticed it made me feel very anxious for some reason.<br/>I will try reading some other Borges&apos; work in the future.</span>
  <span id="freeText10451631091396208229" style="display:none">I can't say I loved this book. However, there were short stories within it I loved, such as The Immortal and The House of Asterion. I simply didn't find most of the short stories interesting. Also, while I was reading this book I noticed it made me feel very anxious for some reason.<br />I will try reading some other Borges' work in the future.</span>
  <a data-text-id="10451631091396208229" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
